QuestData.Title: Ethereum Data
QuestData.Description: Look around you, fleshling. Very close to this transponder should be an Ethereum data cell. Locate that data cell, open it, and retrieve the contents.$B$BBring it back to this transponder at once!
QuestData.LogDescription: The Image of Commander Ameer at the Ethereum Staging Grounds - Ethereum Transponder Zeta - wants you to recover the Ethereum Data Cell.
QuestData.CompletionText: Have you recovered the data cell?
QuestData.RewardText: <You hold the data cell out so Ameer can read the plans.>$B$BNothing... Damn them! They're clever but not as clever as Ameer!$B$BWhat I'm about to ask you to do is quite dangerous. I'll understand if you don't want to continue, fleshling.
